    "long_instructions": "## Journalist - Level 2: One-Shot Prompting\r\n\r\nPractice one-shot prompting through the career of a journalist by adding a single example to help guide the AI’s response.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Try a prompt like the one below, or write a similar one that includes a sample news summary to help the AI understand what you're looking for.\r\n\r\n>Here’s an example of a news summary: “The recent storm in Florida caused significant damage.” Now write a summary about the effects of climate change on coastal cities.\r\n\r\n2. Press **Send**.\r\n3. Read the response you get, paying attention to how the example affects the tone, structure, or detail in the summary.",
